<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog - DollhouseMCP</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Latest updates, tutorials, and insights from the DollhouseMCP team.">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../styles/main.css">
    <style>
        .nav-header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background: var(--color-background);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
            z-index: var(--z-sticky);
            padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        
        .nav-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: var(--space-6);
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: var(--space-6);
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        
        .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active {
            color: var(--color-brand-primary);
        }
        
        body {
            padding-top: 60px;
        }
        
        .blog-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-brand-primary), var(--color-brand-secondary));
            color: white;
            padding: var(--space-16) var(--space-4);
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .blog-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-4);
        }
        
        .blog-post {
            margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
            padding-bottom: var(--space-12);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        }
        
        .blog-post:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .post-date {
            color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
            font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
            margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
        }
        
        .post-title {
            color: var(--color-text-primary);
            font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
            margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        
        .post-title:hover {
            color: var(--color-brand-primary);
        }
        
        .post-excerpt {
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
        }
        
        .read-more {
            color: var(--color-brand-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }
        
        .read-more:hover {
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation Header -->
    <header class="nav-header">
        <div class="nav-left">
            <a href="/"><img src="../icons/Dollhouse-org.png" alt="DollhouseMCP Logo" class="logo" /></a>
            <nav class="nav-links">
                <a href="/">Home</a>
                <a href="/#story">About</a>
                <a href="/blog" class="active">Blog</a>
                <a href="https://github.com/DollhouseMCP/mcp-server" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="toggleTheme()">
            <span class="icon-moon">üåô</span>
            <span class="icon-sun">‚òÄÔ∏è</span>
        </button>
    </header>
    
    <!-- Blog Header -->
    <section class="blog-header">
        <h1>DollhouseMCP Blog</h1>
        <p>Updates, tutorials, and insights from the team</p>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Blog Posts -->
    <div class="blog-container">
        <article class="blog-post">
            <div class="post-date">September 4, 2025</div>
            <a href="/blog/launch-announcement.html" class="post-title">Introducing DollhouseMCP: Vibe Tooling for AI</a>
            <p class="post-excerpt">
                After two years of building with AI tools, we're excited to announce DollhouseMCP - a new way to create persistent, 
                evolving tools using natural language. Learn about our journey from scattered prompts to a comprehensive system that 
                remembers, adapts, and grows with your needs.
            </p>
            <a href="/blog/launch-announcement.html" class="read-more">Read more ‚Üí</a>
        </article>
        
        <article class="blog-post">
            <div class="post-date">Coming Soon</div>
            <h2 class="post-title">Getting Started with DollhouseMCP</h2>
            <p class="post-excerpt">
                A comprehensive guide to setting up DollhouseMCP with Claude Desktop, creating your first personas and skills, 
                and understanding the difference between vibe coding and vibe tooling.
            </p>
        </article>
    </div>
    
    <script>
        function toggleTheme() {
            const html = document.documentElement;
            const currentTheme = html.getAttribute('data-theme');
            const newTheme = currentTheme === 'dark' ? 'light' : 'dark';
            html.setAttribute('data-theme', newTheme);
            localStorage.setItem('theme', newTheme);
        }

        // Load saved theme
        const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'light';
        document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', savedTheme);
    </script>
</body>
</html>